oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Red McEwen Job No. 38875
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: McEwen, Red;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Invoice (No. 3390) for an order placed by Red McEwen for 95 two color window cards (undated) and 5 two color window cards for a performance by Red McEwen at the V. F. W. Club in McMinnville, Tennessee on October 1. Receipt indicates the agreed price, quantity, shipping method, and a description of the posters.
